    <h1>Testimonial: Classical Guitarist with Right Hand Index Finger FD</h1>
    <p>This guitarist experienced severe clenching of the right-hand index finger, which threatened their career. After starting retraining sessions, we utilized customized splints to isolate the movement of the index finger and break the co-contraction patterns.</p>
    
    <p>Within a few months of persistent, slow exercises, the involuntary curling resolved. The guitarist successfully returned to performing high-level classical concert repertoire with full speed and control.</p>

    <blockquote>
      "After being told my condition was permanent, Yogi's structured retraining exercises gave me my right hand back. I am performing in concerts again."
    </blockquote>
    
